quran[110]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On Tippin…óo e dow Jeyaa…óo Makko on Deftere nden O wa…óanaali nde oo√Īaare"
  18,2,"Feewunde fii yo o [Nulaa…óo on] hul…ďinir lepte sattu…óe immorde ka Makko o weltinira gom…óin…ďe …ďen, …ďen …ďe no golla Mo∆ī∆īu…ói …óin wonnde no woodani …ďe Njoddi Mo∆ī∆īiri"
  18,3,"Ko …ďe √Īii…ďoo…ďe e nder makko [Neema on] poomaa"
  18,4,"O rentina …ďen wi\"u…ďe: \"Alla jogitike …ďi…ó…óo"
  18,5,"Ganndal alanaa…ďe e mun, wanaa baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe woodani, mawnii konngol wonungol e yaltude e kunndu…óe ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wowlaali si wanaa fenaande"
  18,6,"Bala jo'o an a tanpinay hoore-maa e dow batteeji ma…ď…ďe, si gom…óinaali ndee Yewtere ka suno"
  18,7,"Menen Men wa…óii ko woni kon ka hoore leydi cu…óaari mayri, fii yo Men jarribo …ďe ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďurata mo∆ī∆īinnde golle"
  18,8,Menen ko Men wa…óoo…ďe ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol yoorungal
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yim…ďe fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi …óin, …óun wonu immorde e Aayeeje Amen hawnii…óe"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaa…ďe …ďen sorunoo ka fammeere, …ďe wi'i: \"Joomi amen okku men immorde ka Maa…óa Hinnayee=yurmeende newinaNaa men kadi e fiyaake amen peewal"
  18,11,Men piyi e dow noppi ma…ď…ďe …óin ka nder fammeere limoore duu…ďi
  18,12,"Refti Men immintini …ďe fii yo Men fen√Īinir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle …óen …ói…ói …ďuri moftude [limoore] ko …ďe √Īii…ďi kon dummunne"
  18,13,"Menen Me…óen fillanaade ma kumpital fii ma…ď…ďe e Goonga, …ďen …óon, ko sukaa…ďe gom…óin…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe Men …ďeydani …ďe Peewal"
  18,14,"Men ha…ď…ďi e dow …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe tuma nde …ďe darinoo, …ďe wi'i: \"Joomi amen ko Jey…óo On kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo rewetee…óo, gom…óii haray men wi'ii ontuma [konngol] fantungol"
  18,15,"∆Āee yim…ďe amen, …ďe jogitike ko woori Mo rewetee…ói, ko haaanunoo ko yo …ďe addu e dow ma…ď…ďe dalil …ďanngu…óo. Ko hommbo …ďuri too√Īude ko foti e on fefindii…óo fenaande o fawi e Alla"
  18,16,"Tuma nde wo…ó…óitino…óon …ďe e ko …ďe rewata kon ko woori Alla, …ďe soroyi ka fammeere Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende Makko nden O newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende"
  18,17,"Hi…óa yi'a naangi ngen si nge ∆īellitike hinge naayora ka fammeere ma…ď…ďe senngo √Īaamo, si hinge mutude nge mutiranay …ďe ka senngo nano, kam…ďe hi…ďe e yaajeende e …óun, …óun ko jeyaa…óun e Aayeeje Alla, on mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewu…óo, kala moO majjini a he…ďantaa mo hettu…óo fewnoowo. @Corrected"
  18,18,"Hi…óa sikka …ďe ko …ďe finu…ďe, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe …óaanii…ďe, Me…óen waylitira …ďe senngo √Īaamo e senngo nano, rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun no fonti kay…óe mun …óen ka dammbugal, si a ∆īellitike e ma…ď…ďe a huccitayno e ma…ď…ďe dogaa a heewayno kulol immorde e ma…ď…ďe"
  18,19,"Ko nii Men immintiniri …ďe fii yo …ďe lanndondir hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, wi'oowo wi'i immorde e ma…ď…ďe: \"No foti hewde ko √Īii…ďu…óon?\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Men √Īii…ďii √Īallal maa go…ó…óun e √Īallal.\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko √Īii…ďu…óon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon wonndude e …óii kaaki=ceede mon …óoo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri laa…ďude √Īaamitee, yo o addan on √Īaametee immorde e on …óon, yo o molto wata gooto so'u fii mon"
  18,20,"Pellet, kam…ďe si …ďe ∆īellitike e mon …ďe rajmay on, maa…óun …ďe rutta on e laawol ma…ď…ďe ngol, ontuma hara on maletaake poomaa"
  18,21,"Ko nii Men yaltiniri fii ma…ď…ďe, fii yo …ďe anndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nden ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darngal ngal sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde …ďe poo…óondiraynoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe fiyaake ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe wi'i: \"Mahee e hoore ma…ď…ďe maadi, ko Joomi ma…ď…ďe woni Anndu…óo fii Ma…ď…ďe.\" ∆Āen foolu…ďe e fiyaake mu'un wi'i: \"Men jogitoto e dow ma…ď…ďe Juulirde"
  18,22,"Aray …ďe wi'a: \"Ko …ďe tato naya…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun.\" ∆Āe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ďe njowo njeega…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun ko fampaangol ka ni…ďe.\" ∆Āe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ďe njee…ói…óo njeetata…ďo ma…ď…ďe ko rawaandu ma…ď…ďe ndun.\" Maaku: \"Ko Joomi an woni Anndu…óo limoore ma…ď…ďe, anndaa …ďe si wanaa see…óaa…ďe.\" Wata a wennju fii ma…ď…ďe si wanaa yewtere fee√Īunde, wata a lanndo fii ma…ď…ďe hay e gooto e ma…ď…ďe"
  18,23,"Wata a wi'an huunde: \"Min mi wa…óay …óun janngo"
  18,24,"Si wanaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maa…óa si a yejjitii, maaku: \"No tijjaa nde Joomi an Fewnan mi ko …ďuri …ďadaade immorde e …óun Peewal"
  18,25,"∆Āe √Īii…ďi ka fammeere ma…ď…ďe duu…ďi teeme…ó…óe tati, …ďe …ďeydi jeenay"
  18,26,"Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko …ďe √Īii…ďi, ko Kanko heeranii ko wirnii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa Makko e ko naniri, alanaa …ďe gaanin Makko gi…óo, O kafidaa ka √Ďaawoore Makko hay e gooto"
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maa…óa kon immorde e Deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko …óin, a he…ďataa gaanin Makko fattorde"
  18,28,"Tabintin wonkii maa…óa kin wonndude e …ďen noddoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe hi…ďe faandii Jaati Makko Kin, wata gite maa …óe yawtu gaayi ma…ď…ďe hara hi…óa faandii cu…óaari ngurdan aduna, wota a …óofto on mo Men welsindini …ďernde mun gaayi jantagol Men o jokki belee…óe makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare"
  18,29,"Maaku Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi mon, mono faalaa yo o gom…óin mono faalaa yo o yeddu, Menen Men heblanii too√Īoo…ďe …ďen Yiite no hunnditi …ďe …óen…óe magge …óen si …ďe …óa…ď…ďii faabo, …ďe faaboree ndiyan wa'u…óan wa sila taynaa…óo …óan ju…óa geece …óen, bonii njaram bonii werde"
  18,30,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óin…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin, Menen Men yeebataa njoddi kala mo∆ī∆īin…óo golle"
  18,31,"∆Āen …óon no woodani …ďe Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal can…ói no ila ley ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe cu…óiree ton immorde e jawe kanŇče …ďe …ďornoo conci haaki…óu…ói …óewlu…ói e jalbu…ói ko …ďe so…ď…ďindii…ďe=tuugiibe ton e hoore julle, mo∆ī∆īii mbarjaari mo∆ī∆īii kadi fowtorde"
  18,32,"fiyan …ďe misal,wor…ďe …ói…óo Men wa…óani go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe gese …ói…ói inab Menhunndintini =hurliride …óe tamarooje Men wa…ói hakkunde majje remuru"
  18,33,"∆äen gese …ói…ói kala addi √Īaametee majje, …óe too√Īaali hay e huunde e …óun, Men seeki hakkunde majje [gese …óen …ói…ói] caangol"
  18,34,"Wonani mo dim…óe, o wi'ani wonndii…óo makko on tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Min mi…óo …ďurumaa jawdi e teddude gorol"
  18,35,"O naati ka ngesa makko tawi ko o too√Īu…óo hoore-makko, o wi'i: \"Mi sikkaa mbaa re'ay poomaa\". @Corrected"
  18,36,"Mi sikkaa kdai Darngal ngal daroto, mi woondii si mi artira le ka Joomi an, maa mi tawu sanne, waylitorde …ďurnde mba mo∆ī∆īude"
  18,37,"Wonndii…óo makko on wi'ani mo, tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Enee, a yeddii On Tagu…óo ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e to…ď…ďere [maniiyu] refti O fonndumaa gorko"
  18,38,"Kono min ko Kanko Alla woni Joomi an, mi kafidataa e Joomi an hay gooto"
  18,39,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde naatu…óaa ka ngesa maa…óa wi'aa: \"Ko Alla muuyi kon doole alaa si wanaa Alla\". Si a yi'ii lan, min mi…óo …ďurumaa fan…óude jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe"
  18,40,No jortaa nde Joomi an okkoyta lan mo∆ī∆īere …ďurnde ngesa maa mban O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu mba wonta boowal …ďowrungal
  18,41,"Maa…óun ndiyan mabba …óan wonta …ďee…ďu…óan, hara a hattantaake …óa…ď…ďugol …óan"
  18,42,"Dim…óe makko …óen bonnaa o weeti himo waylita newe makko …óen e dow ko o nafki kon e mabba, tawi kammba ko fukkiimba e da∆ī∆īe mabba, himo wi'a: \"Ee jalla min, hara mi kafidaano e Joomi an hay e gooto"
  18,43,"Laatanaaki mo fedde nde no walla mo gaanin Alla, o wonaali foolu…óo"
  18,44,No ton Giggol Alla Goongawol ngol ko Kanngo mo∆ī∆īi mbarjaari mo∆ī∆īi battane
  18,45,"Fiyan …ďe misal ngurdan aduna …óan no wa'i wa ndiyan Men jippini…óan immorde ka kammu jillondiri e majjan pu…ói leydi ndin, …ói wonti muncii…ói keneeli no jaroo…ói, Alla wonii ko O Hattan…óo e dow kala huunde"
  18,46,"Jawdi ndin e …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe …ďen ko cu…óaari ngurndan aduna, mo∆ī∆īi heddotoo…ói …óin ko …óin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude mbarjaari ka Joomi maa…óa e mo∆ī∆īude yela"
  18,47,"√Ďannde Men na…ďata pelle …óen a yi'ay leydi ndin ko fee√Īundi, Men moo…ďa …ďe Men accataa immorde e ma…ď…ďe hay e gooto"
  18,48,"∆Āe holliree ka Joomi maa [ko …ďe] saffewol, [O Daalana …ďe] gom…óii on arii e Amen wano Men tagirnoo on non, ka laawol aranol, ko woni on aa∆īino wonnde Men wa…óanaali on fodoore"
  18,49,"Deftere nden wallinee, a yi'ay bom…ďe …ďen ko hul…ďe ko woni kon e mayre, …ďe wi'a: \"Ee bone amen, ko he…ďi ndee deftere nde …óalataa tosokun wanaa njanun si wanaa nde moftii …óun, …ďe tawa ko …ďe golli kon no wee…ďitaa, Joomi maa…óa too√Īataa hay e gooto"
  18,50,"Tuma nde Men wi'annoo Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen: \"Sujjanee Aadama, …ďe sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o laatike jeyaa…óo e jinnaaji …óin o yalti e Yamiroore Joomi makko. E on jogitoto mo e …ďi…ó…ďe makko …ďen yim…ďe gaanin An, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe ay…ďe mo'on, bonanii too√Īoo…ďe …ďen battudi"
  18,51,"Mi tawnaali …ďe tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin wanaa tagugol ko'e ma…ď…ďe kadi, Mi wonaali jogitotoo…óo majjinoo…ďe …ďen sembinoo…ďe. @Corrected"
  18,52,"E √Īannde O Daalata: \"Noddee kafidaa…ďe An …ďen, …ďen …ďe aa∆īi…óon, …ďe nodda …ďe, …ďe jaabotaako …ďe Men wa…ói hakkunde ma…ď…ďe halkorde"
  18,53,"Bom…ďe …ďen yi'a Yiite ngen …ďe fellita wonnde kam…ďe ko …ďe ukketee…ďe e magge, …ďe he…ďataa gaayi magge yiltorde"
  18,54,"Gom…óii Men fensitanii yim…ďe …ďen e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala misal, ne…ó…óanke on wonii himo …ďuri kala huunde wennjugol"
  18,55,"Ha…óaali yim…ďe …ďen nde …ďe gom…óinta …ďe insinanoo Joomi ma…ď…ďe tuma nde Peewal ngal arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa nde arata e ma…ď…ďe sunna aran…ďe …ďen maa…óun nde arata e ma…ď…ďe lepte …óen ko …óe fee√Īu…óe"
  18,56,"Men Nuliraali Nulaa…ďe …ďen si wanaa ko weltinoo…ďe e jertinoo…ďe, …ďen heefer…ďe hi…ďe wennjana meere nden fii yo …ďe fuynir nde Goonga kan, …ďe jogitii Aayeeje An …óen e ko …ďe jertiniraa kon jalnori"
  18,57,"Alaa fotay…óo too√Īude on waajuraa…óo Aayeeje Joomi makko o …óuurii=fali e gaayi majje o yejjiti ko juu…óe makko …óen ardini kon. Menen Men wa…óii e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen cokoo…óe fii wota …ďe faamu nde, ka noppi ma…ď…ďe kadi pahu, hay si a noddii …ďe faade e Peewal …ďe feewataa ontuma haapoomaa"
  18,58,"Ko Joomi mon woni Surroowo ko O Jom Hinnayee on, sinndo O nangitirno …ďe ko …ďe faggitii kon O yaccinanayno …ďe lepte …óen, ko woni, no woodani …ďe fodoore …ďe he…ďataa gaanin mayre fattorde"
  18,59,"∆äen ca'e, Men halkuno …ďe tuma nde …ďe too√Īunoo Men wa…óani halkeede ma…ď…ďe nden Fodoore"
  18,60,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo sagataa makko on: \"Mi seerataa haa mi yottoo ka fottirde maaje …óen …ói…ói, maa…óun mi wuloo jamaanu"
  18,61,"Tuma nde …ďe yottoyinoo hakkonde majje …ďe yejjiti linngil ma…ď…ďe ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo wuddere"
  18,62,"Nde …ďe lummbunoo o [Muusaa] maakani sagataa makko on: \"Anndanii en sojjaari=bottaari men ndin, gom…óii en hawrii e nduu yaadu men …óoo tampere"
  18,63,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii, nde soruno…óen ka fetere, min mi yejjuno linngil ngil, yejjintinaali lan fii maggil si wanaa Seytaane nde mi anndita ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo no hawnori"
  18,64,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko …óon ko won…óen …óa…ď…ďude kon [woni], …ďe ruttii e …ďatteeji ma…ď…ďe fillitagol"
  18,65,"∆Āe tawoyi jeyaa…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Amen Men Okki mo Hinnayee immorde ka Amen, Men Anndini mo immorde e Amen Ganndal"
  18,66,"Muusaa maakani mo: \"Enee [a accay] mi jokkete fii yo a anndinan go…ó…óun e ko anndina…óaa kon Peewal"
  18,67,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Pellet, an a hattantaake mu√Īal wonndugol e an"
  18,68,Ko honno mun√Īuretaa e dow kon ko a hu…ďindoraa …óun ganndal
  18,69,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"A taway lan si Alla Muuyi ko mi mun√Īii…óo, mi yeddataa yamiroore maa"
  18,70,"O maaki: \"Si a jokkay lam wata a lanndo lan gaayi huunde haa mi yeewte immorde e mayre janta"
  18,71,"∆Āe yahi haa nde …ďe wa…ó…óinoo ka laana o yulika, [Muusaa] maaki: \"A yulii ka fii yo ka yoolu yim…ďe makka?! gom…óii a addii huunde mawnde"
  18,72,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake mu√Īal wonndugol e am"
  18,73,"[Muusaa] maaki: wata a jogoran ko mi yijjiti kon, wata a hewtinan e fiyaake an on satteende"
  18,74,"∆Āe yahi haa nde …ďe fottunoo e suka o wari mo! O maakani [mo]: \"E a waru wonkii laa…ďuki tanaa [yo…ďtanagol] wonkii, gom…óii a addii huunde a√Īiinde"
  18,75,"[Khadiru] wi'i: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake mu√Īal wonndugol e an"
  18,76,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Si mi lanndike ma gaayi huunde …ďaawo …óii, haray wata a wonndino e an, gom…óii a timminii nganto e an"
  18,77,"∆Āe yahi haa …ďe yaltiti e yim…ďe saare, …ďe …óa…ď…ďiri …ďe √Īaametee …ďe salii wernude …ďe, …ďe tawi e nder mayre maadi faalaa fukkaade [Khadiru] o darnindi , o [Muusaa] maaki: \"Sinno a yi…óuno a ∆īettayno njoddi e …óun"
  18,78,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Ko …óum woni seedigal hakku- nde an e ma'a, aray mi yiito maa firo kon ko a hattananooka mun√Īaade e dow mun"
  18,79,"Si ko laana kan, ka laatanike miskinee…ďe gollo- …ďe ka maayo, mi faalaa aybinnde ka, hari laatike …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe lam…óo himo nannga kala laana o ja…ďta"
  18,80,"Si ko suka on maw…ďe makko …ďen wonii gom…óim…ďe , men huli wata o fawu …ďe bewre e keeferaaku"
  18,81,Men faalaa nde Joomi ma…ď…ďe wa…ótitanta …ďe …ďur…óo mo mo∆ī∆īude laa…ďu…óo e …ďur…óo …ďattaade yurmeende
  18,82,"Si ko maadi ndin, ndi laatanino sukaa…ďe …ói…óo won…óu…ďe ka saare, laatii ley mayri ngalu ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo, hari baaba ma…ď…ďe laatinoke mo∆ī∆īo, Joomi maa…óa Faalaa nde …ďe yottotoo sagatalaaku ma…ď…ďe, O yaltina ngalu ma…ď…ďe ngun […óum] ko Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, mi wa…óiraali …óum e yamirooree an, …óum ko firo kon ko a hattanaali mun√Īaade e dow mun"
  18,83,"Hi…ďe fa'umaa lanndaade fii Julqarnayni, maaku: \"Aray mi jannga e taweede mon e …óun janta"
  18,84,"Menen, Men wee…ďinanno mo ka leydi, Men Okki mo immorde e kala huunde sabu"
  18,85,O jokki sabu
  18,86,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka mutirde naange ngen o tawi hinge muta e loope …ďaleeje, o tawi ton yim…ďe : Men wi'i: \"Ko an yo jom galaa…ói …ói…ói, ko si a leptay maa…óun si a jogitoto e ma…ď…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi"
  18,87,"O wi'i: Si tawii ko on too√Īu…óo aray men lepta mo, refti o ruttee ka Joomi makko O lepta mo lepte a√Īii…óe"
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gom…óin…óo o golli ko mo∆ī∆īi no woodani mo njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īiri ndin, aray Men wi'ana mo e fiyaake Amen on neweende"
  18,89,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,90,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka ∆īellitorde naange ngen, o tawi hinge ∆īellitoo e dow yim…ďe, Men wa…óanaali …ďe gaanin magge heedo"
  18,91,"Ko wano nii, gom…óii Men hu…ďindike ko woni kon ka makko e ganndal. @Corrected"
  18,92,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,93,Haa nde o yottinoo hakkunde heedooji …óin …ói…óio tawi gaanin majji yim…ďe …ďe …óe…ďataa faamude konngol
  18,94,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko an Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ko bonnoo…ďe ka leydi. Enee, men wa…óante ngeenaari fii yo a wa…óu hakkunde amen e ma…ď…ďe heedo"
  18,95,"O wi'i: \"Ko Joomi am wee…ďinani lan kon …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, walliree lan doole mi wa…óa hakkunde mo'on e ma…ď…ďe heedo"
  18,96,"Addanee lam kunte njam…óe haa nde o feppi- ndirnoo hakkunde na…óe …óen …ói…ói, o wi'i: \"Wifee haa nde o wa…óunoo …óum yiite, o wi'i: addanee lam sila mi wancina e dow mun"
  18,97,"∆Āe hattantaake ∆īellitagol ndi, …ďe hattantaake kadi yulugol ndi"
  18,98,"O wi'i: …óum …óoo ko Yurmeende immornde e Joomi am, si Fodoore Joomi am nden arii O wa…óay [heedo] ngon …óiggungo, Fodoore Joomi am nden laatike ko nde Goonga"
  18,99,"Men …óala yoga e ma…ď…ďe nden √Īalnde no yolloo e yoga, wuttaa ka allaadu Men moo…ďa …ďe moo…ďudee"
  18,100,Men wee…ďitanay(holliray) Jahannama nden √Īannde yeddu…ďe …ďen wee…ďitugol=holllirgol
  18,101,"∆Āen …ďe gite mun laatii e wirngallo gaayi janta An, …ďe laati…ďe hattantaake nanugol"
  18,102,"Enee, …ďen yeddu…ďe sikku …ďe jogoto jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen gaanin Am, Menen Men heblanii Jahannama on fii yeddu…ďe…ďen wona werde. @Corrected"
  18,103,"Maaku: \"Taw si men hupitay on fii …ďur…ďe hayrude(pertude) golle"
  18,104,Ko …ďen …ďe golle mun yeebii ka ngurdan aduna hara kam…ďe hi…ďe sikka hi…ďe mo∆ī∆īinnde golle
  18,105,"Ko …ďen woni yeddu…ďe Aayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen e hawroygol e Makko, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen bone Men √Īii…ďinantaa…ďe √Ďalnde Darngal ∆Āetu"
  18,106,"Jahannama ko …óun woni njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe, sabu ko …ďe yeddi kon …ďe jogitii Aayeeje Am …óen e Nulaa…ďe Am …ďen jalkitde"
  18,107,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin laatanto …ďe Aljannaaji Firdawsi Werdi(jipporde)"
  18,108,"Ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe nder ton, …ďe …óa…ď…ďataa gaayi makko waylitorde"
  18,109,"Maaku: \"Sinno maayo ngo laatino ndawa fii Daaluyeeji Joomi am …óin, maayo ngon re'ayno ko adii nde re'ata Daaluyeeji Joomi am …óin, sinno Men addii yeru maggo e …ďeydude"
  18,110,"Maaku: \"Pellet min, ko mi …ďanndinnke yeru mon, no wahayineede e am. Pellet, Rewetee…óo mon On ko Rewetee…óo Gooto, kala jortii…óo hawroyde e Joomi makko yo o gollu golle mo∆ī∆īe wata o kafidu e dewal Joomi makko hay e gooto"